        @Query(value = &quot;UPDATE my_entity SET my_field = :newValue WHERE id IN :ids RETURNING id&quot;, nativeQuery = true)
        List&lt;Long&gt; updateMyFieldByIdsAndReturnIds(@Param(&quot;newVal&quot;) String newVal, @Param(&quot;ids&quot;) List&lt;Long&gt; ids);
    }

Note that the `nativeQuery` attribute of the `@Query` annotation is set to `true` to indicate that we are using a native SQL query instead of a JPQL query. Also, make sure to use the correct syntax for your database when using native queries.

